    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057870/extras/17fde5b87f6d0b3a091e74c919e3fbae.avif?t=1736728521\" width=614 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>序章和正式版的区别</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>地图：序章有2个岛屿，正式版有5个。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>农作物：序章会包含8种农作物，正式版还有8种农作物可以在游戏中解锁。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>模式：序章有普通模式，正式版有专家模式、随机模式和无尽模式。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收藏：您将能够在序章中解锁新的头像和标记。 （在正式版中你还可以购买更多农作物。）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>统计数据：序章中没有成就，并且您不会在排行榜上获得一席之地。 </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>进度：所有进度都将延续至正式版本。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057870/extras/c334353e47cf316588d1b7153bbcd5d1.webp?t=1736728521\" width=615 height=62 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057870/extras/fc8aa0fc6a292c13d3b935cc23243d20.avif?t=1736728521\" width=480 height=140 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057870/extras/1.gif?t=1736728521\" /></span><strong>每一轮你都以特定的模式种植农作物。正确种植它们将使它们焕发活力！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057870/extras/581939cf5ff87390acfa2d440ed26a96.webp?t=1736728521\" width=615 height=62 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057870/extras/bfad420e7a4e67e0f5e4c456ae147940.avif?t=1736728521\" width=500 height=156 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057870/extras/4b0e184892592a99d6750e01d8d54ba1.poster.avif?t=1736728521\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057870/extras/4b0e184892592a99d6750e01d8d54ba1.webm?t=1736728521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057870/extras/4b0e184892592a99d6750e01d8d54ba1.mp4?t=1736728521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>种植后，战略性地移动你的蔬菜，以全新自走棋风格抵御老鼠。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057870/extras/234c4ef90419998eb269fbcd1ced04dc.webp?t=1736728521\" width=615 height=62 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057870/extras/9e58514e31c48f0c99970a858109479e.poster.avif?t=1736728521\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057870/extras/9e58514e31c48f0c99970a858109479e.webm?t=1736728521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057870/extras/9e58514e31c48f0c99970a858109479e.mp4?t=1736728521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>解锁多种新作物！、头像和标记。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5 个不同的岛屿，有独特的头目和敌人。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解锁专家模式和无尽模式。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全球排行榜。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成就和进展跟踪。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>具有随机场布局和特殊增益场的无尽策略。</strong></p>",
